<body>
	<header>
		<h1 class="glitch">xenxier</h1>
		<h2 class="glitch">zen-zi-er</h2>
	</header>
	<div id="whoami" class="content">
		<h1>who?</h1>
		<p>I am a programmer - I give a computer words, and then the computer does things based on the words I give it. Sometimes these things turn out pretty great, but a lot of the time I end up <span class="glitch">deleting</span> a lot of the work I do.<br></br>Basically, I'm a guy who program things because I think it's fun.</p>
	</div>
	<div id="projects" class="content">
		<h1>what?</h1>
		<p>I have created many projects in the past, and the ones which I finish to a point where I feel comfortable sharing them with the world end up <span class="glitch"><a href="https://github.com/benjamingwynn">here</a></span>, at my GitHub.</p>
	</div>
	<div id="lang" class="content">
		<h1>how?</h1>
		<p>I can program in a variety of programming languages. But I am most comfortable with Java, HTML 5, CSS 3, Javascript, VBA and Lua - as these are the ones I use most commonly.</p>
	</div>
	<div id="contact" class="content">
		<h1>awesome.</h1>
		<p>If you wish to contact me, you can do so via <span class="glitch"><a href="mailto:xenxier@gmail.com">this link</a></span> to my email address.</p>
	</div>
